d technical personnel are expected to continue increasing for the foreseeable future. \n*   **Uncertainty of Returns:** Management notes there is uncertainty around how long scaling laws (the empirical observation that model performance improves with increased compute, data, and model size) will continue to hold, and there can be no assurance that returns on AI investments will be adequate to justify the capital deployed.',
